snippet.title: In the Loop: Duterte's bank account; Melai's answer

localized.description:
TJ Manotoc keeps us in the loop on Davao City Mayor Rodrido Duterte's bank account, Melai Cantiveros defending her daughter, and Alyssa Valdez and Kiefer Ravena's restaurant.
